media:group.media:title: Learn French Adjectives [before after]
media:group.media:description:
Adjectives in French, part 2. In english the adjectives are always before the noun but in French it is different, sometimes before, or after and even both, sometimes the meaning is not the same when the adjective is before or after, we are going to see the BAGS and the FNCM rules. I hope you will enjoy.

Visit: https://www.frenchspanishonline.com it is free
